   Typical 'Wet' Sprinkler

   The Consumer Products Safety Commission (CPSC) and the Central
   Sprinkler Company have announced the recall of the company's sprinkler
   heads with rubber O-ring seals. wedge More information about the
   Central Sprinkler Recall  Another information bulletin was issued on
   9-27-01, click here to view

   Replacement information available at the Central Sprinkler Company
   Sprinkler Replacement site. www.sprinklerreplacement.com
